definitions.definition: An inland traditional county of Wales , bounded to the north by Montgomeryshire and Shropshire , to the east by Herefordshire , to the south by Brecknockshire and to the west by Cardiganshire .

main_definition: An inland traditional county of Wales , bounded to the north by Montgomeryshire and Shropshire , to the east by Herefordshire , to the south by Brecknockshire and to the west by Cardiganshire .
